vacy-policy.html. If you object to your Information being transferred or used in this way please do not use the Website.<br><div align="justify">&nbsp;<br>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div align="justify">7A. Your Consent: By using the Site and/ or by providing your information, you consent to the collection and use of the information you disclose on the Site by Honey bunny dot in.com in accordance with Honey bunny dot in.com Privacy Policy. <br>\n</div>\n<br>\n</div>\n<div id="81c72a6d-7311-4b3c-b218-ffdf7d258e05" component_namespace="titleElement" component_type="Title" class="epan-component" style="padding-top: 1%;" contenteditable="true">  	<h4 id="idservices">8. Payments\n</h4> </div>\n<div id="eadc0ada-6c2f-4d3f-b72f-24104556d0f4" component_namespace="textElement" component_type="Text" class="editor epan-component editor-attached" style="padding-top: 1%; padding-left: 2%;" contenteditable="true"><div align="justify">Payments for items on the Website can be made through the electronic or through Cash on delivery transactions, as may be permitted by Honey bunny dot in.com to the website seller(s) in its sole discretion. We process online payments on merchants behalf and send the money to merchant after deducting our service fees. Merchants does not have to deal with online payments as we take care of it. All we need from merchants some banking and accounting information for us to set-up online bank transfer account. We have a weekly payment cycle. Every Friday money (order final value minus our service fees) will be electronically transferred for all Completed Orders occurred two weeks back to your mentioned bank account. <br><br>\n</div></div>\n<div id="81c72a6d-7311-4b3c-b218-ffdf7d258e05" component_namespace="titleElement" component_type="Title" class="epan-component" style="padding-top: 1%;" contenteditable="true">  	<h4 id="idservices">9. Breach\n</h4> </div>\n<div id="eadc0ada-6c2f-4d3f-b72f-24104556d0f4" component_namespace="textElement" component_type="Text" class=