0.35cm" align="justify">Irrespective of what product or from which merchant you buy Honey Bunny Dot In at, we are on your side in terms of giving the best online shopping experience and complete buyer protection.<br><br>Our rigorous merchant approval process ensures that our buyers can be assured on all aspects of product purchase, be it authenticity, quality, manufacturer warranty, or the price. Our merchants typically are successful retailers or brand owners or authorized dealers who have earned credibility and customer loyalty through years of excellence in building customer experience in the offline environment. So as a buyer you can be confident that you are buying the reliable merchants. Honey Bunny Dot In brings the best from all India together on one platform.<br><br>We not only help our merchants reach to a larger market on a reliable platform but also to increase business multifold within the online space. This is done through a host of business management tools, effective marketing.<br>&nbsp;<br>You may be a buyer or a seller but there is one thing in common that Honey Bunny Dot In promises to both, unmatched online experience no matter which side of the transaction you are. Welcome to the marketplace!<br><br>With our customer centric approach we provide the best online shopping experience to our customers – starting from the great selection, low price, fast delivery, simple interface, and ending with the best customer service you have ever experienced.<br></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.35cm" align="justify">Honey Bunny Dot In, is also rendering its services in:<br>1. Website Development and Search Engine Optimization (SEO) techniques<br>2. Production House (Films, Video Advertisements, Corporate Videos etc)<br>3. Advertising and Marketing – Outdoor <br>4. Public Relations and Event Management<br><br>The firms is an concept of an entertaining fusion of social networking and e-commerce website, developed by two budding entrepreneurs, Jashwant.k.Salvi and Ishaan Bhatnagar, Computer graduates.<br><style type="text/css">P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); widows: 2; orphans: 2; }A:link { color: rgb(0, 0, 255); }</style></p>\n\n </div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n<div style="font-size: 100%; background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% transparent; border: medium none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 1154px; height: 20px; float: none; position: relative; z-index: auto; top: 0px; left: 0px; bottom: 0px; right: 0px;" class="ui-effects-wrapper"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'cursor: move;', '2014-04-28 08:09:36', '2014-05-01 13:04:20', 'public', 12);
